      <title>Markdown入门</title>
      <link href="/posts/12680/"/>
      <url>/posts/12680/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="以下为效果展示"><a href="#以下为效果展示" class="headerlink" title="以下为效果展示"></a>以下为效果展示</h1><h2 id="H2"><a href="#H2" class="headerlink" title="H2"></a>H2</h2><h3 id="H3"><a href="#H3" class="headerlink" title="H3"></a>H3</h3><p><strong>bold text</strong><br><em>italicized text</em></p><ol><li>First item</li><li>Second item</li><li>Third item、</li></ol><ul><li>First item</li><li>Second item</li><li>Third item<br><code>code</code></li></ul><p><img src="/image.jpg" alt="alt text"></p><p><a href="https://markdown.com.cn/basic-syntax/">Markdown教程官网</a></p><table><thead><tr><th>Syntax</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Header</td><td>Title</td></tr><tr><td>Paragraph</td><td>Text</td></tr></tbody></table><blockquote><p>blockquote</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">{ </span><br><span class="line">  "firstName": "John",</span><br><span class="line">  "lastName": "Smith",</span><br><span class="line">  "age": 25</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>Here’s a sentence with a footnote. [^1]</p><p>[^1]: This is the footnote.</p><h3 id="My-Great-Heading-1"><a href="#My-Great-Heading-1" class="headerlink" title="My Great Heading {1}"></a>My Great Heading {1}</h3><p><del>The world is flat.</del></p><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> Write the press release</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Update the website</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Contact the media</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Markdown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
